headline.main: Several Thousand People Attend Concert-Protest in Serbia
headline.print_headline: Several Thousand People Attend Concert-Protest in Serbia

lead_paragraph: Several thousand people have protested the cancellation of a popular singer's concert in Serbia, allegedly over his support for a liberal opposition candidate before next month's presidential election.
